  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/5c1cd7310bd47410431e2b36f24d0c04.avif?t=1748787182\" width=613 height=77 /></span><br><br>Wedding Witch is a rogue-like game that involves exploring randomly generated maps, fighting against hordes of devils, and finding the Succubus's potions.<br><br>The Succubus's potions are hidden somewhere in a dark forest filled with devils. Solve various tasks in order to find the potions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/4b7805052e3dd21451770894fb5b41a0.avif?t=1748787182\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><br>Drinking the Succubus's potions will make the witch's body transform. What kind of witch do you desire?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/20348b9c21334d65d9ef96e92f00633a.avif?t=1748787182\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>The witch gains access to new spells whenever she drinks the Succubus's potions. Create your own spell combinations!<br><br>Magical flowers containing mysterious energies bloom in the labyrinthine forest. Add them to your bouquet and gain new powers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/e839d03a3618603c7e81f9f0377925ab.avif?t=1748787182\" width=616 height=340 /></span><br><br>Find the Succubus's potions, escape the forest, and earn your happy ending!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/5c1cd7310bd47410431e2b36f24d0c04.avif?t=1748787182\" width=613 height=77 /></span><br><br>Wedding Witch is a rogue-like game that involves exploring randomly generated maps, fighting against hordes of devils, and finding the Succubus's potions.<br><br>The Succubus's potions are hidden somewhere in a dark forest filled with devils. Solve various tasks in order to find the potions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/4b7805052e3dd21451770894fb5b41a0.avif?t=1748787182\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><br>Drinking the Succubus's potions will make the witch's body transform. What kind of witch do you desire?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/20348b9c21334d65d9ef96e92f00633a.avif?t=1748787182\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>The witch gains access to new spells whenever she drinks the Succubus's potions. Create your own spell combinations!<br><br>Magical flowers containing mysterious energies bloom in the labyrinthine forest. Add them to your bouquet and gain new powers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529820/extras/e839d03a3618603c7e81f9f0377925ab.avif?t=1748787182\" width=616 height=340 /></span><br><br>Find the Succubus's potions, escape the forest, and earn your happy ending!",
